title: Tin Foil Hat Ep 11(Bonus Episode): Alien Agenda With Trez Mala
description:
Welcome to a bonus episode of Sam Tripoli's Tin Foil Hat. On this episode I am joined by Vegas comedian, Trez Mala, and we discuss...
1. Alien visitation and genetic manipulation
2. Devine Right of Kings
3. Mythicism
4. Symbolism
5. Alien Agenda/NWO
